Package: MSMICA
Type: Package
Title: Mega scale metabolomics identification through connections of untargeted metabolomics data (MSMICA)
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Jiada", family = "Zhan", middle = "", "jzha832@emory.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2480-8760")
    )
  )
Maintainer: Jiada (James) Zhan <jzha832@emory.edu>
Date: 2024-06-27
Description: MSMICA uses experimentally optimized parameters, including adduct formations, adduct correlations, enzyme-based precursor-product correlations, and isotope correlations, to quantify the confidence of metabolite identification with a probability approach. The output is a unique list of identified metabolites with the one adduct form, m/z, and retention time assigned.
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
